/*
Reset the warp target location and set it a new one.  This code should be used
in the "Set Target" button for each of the available destinations. The control
panel holder should be attached so it can be displayed, and the motion object
"TARGET RESET", which will trigger the script "target_reset" to remove all
possible target states.
*/

TOUCHES: /THEY TARGET RESET /WAITS 0.25  /SHOWS CONTROL PANEL /THEY ARE TARGET MAIN
